data.description: Welcome to this charming and updated Ranch! This delightful home offers the perfect blend of cozy comfort and modern convenience, with an inviting open floor plan and an abundance of natural light. Step inside to discover freshly painted interiors complemented by new 'Antique Wood' LVP flooring. The heart of the home shines with brand new marbled quartz countertops, sleek stainless-steel appliances, and rich cherry-toned cabinets in the kitchen. Two spacious bedrooms, adorned with ceiling fans for added comfort, provide peaceful havens for rest and relaxation. Enjoy the renovated bathroom, with contemporary fixtures as well as the convenient laundry closet which comes complete with a washer and dryer. You'll appreciate the updated windows, electrical, new smart thermostat and newly paint exterior. Outside, a sprawling backyard awaits, beckoning you to enjoy endless hours of outdoor fun and entertainment. With a large shed for storage and a garden bed for cultivating your green thumb, the possibilities are endless. Nestled in a prime location close to shopping destinations like Costco and Target, as well as a variety of restaurants, this home offers the ultimate blend of convenience and effortless living. Don't miss your chance to make this wonderful home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the joy of ranch-style living at its finest!
